Blog Management System
A blog management system where users can create, read, update, and delete blog posts. The backend is built using Node.js, Express, and MySQL.

Features
User registration and authentication
CRUD operations for blog posts
Commenting on blog posts
Relationship management between users, blog posts, and comments
Technologies Used
Node.js
Express.js
MySQL
Sequelize ORM
Postman (for API testing)
Getting Started
Prerequisites
Ensure you have the following installed:

Node.js
MySQL
XAMPP (optional for MySQL management)
